dct_title_s: Plan of the County of the City of Glasgow: constructed for the Post Office Directory
dct_description_sm: John Bartholomew & Son Ltd. The Geographical Institute. Inset: Large scale section of Central Glasgow (1:12,672 ). Municipal boundaries are indicated. "The plan is divided into half-mile squares. Map no.: 967.
